<quantity id="4CD2E99CFFC0FFDDFDE1FD47FD5EC799" box="[582,698,702,723]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="90" unit="mm" value="0.3" valueMax="0.5" valueMin="0.1">0.1–0.5 mm</quantity>
long in the other Thai taxa).
</paragraph>
